  "title": "Key Account Manager (Supply Chain Financing, Factoring, Financial Solutions)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Manage and grow relationships with key corporate accounts through structured engagement and account development strategies.</li><li>Identify and capture revenue opportunities in Supply Chain Financing, Factoring, and related financial solutions through cross-selling initiatives.</li><li>Drive strategic collaborations and referral partnerships that contribute to sustainable revenue growth.</li><li>Conduct regular client reviews and onsite engagements to ensure strong account performance and high client satisfaction.</li><li>Act as the primary point of contact for strategic customers, overseeing issue resolution and service excellence.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><ul><li>Degree in Business, Finance, or equivalent</li><li>At least 4 years of experience in <strong>corporate or SME banking, or equivalent roles within financial services.</strong></li><li>Working knowledge of supply chain finance and factoring products.</li><li>Strong stakeholder management, negotiation, and communication skills.</li></ul><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701<br />Registration: R21100996</p>",
